1055 Partners LLC






Senior Managing Director, Head of Investment Banking

                                    Prior - 2016                


MLV & Co. LLC


                  Founded in 2010, MLV & Co. LLC is a broker/dealer located in New York City. The firm is a direct subsidiary of FBR Capital Markets Holdings, Inc. and their ultimate parent is FBR & Co. (NASDAQ: FBRC), which acquired the firm in 2015. Their research focuses on small to mid-sized companies with disruptive technologies that have the potential to drive significant market changes. MLV & Co.'s coverage universe includes the life sciences, oil & gas and metals & mining sectors.                




Senior Managing Director

                                    Prior - 2016                


FBR & Co.


                  FBR & Co. provides investment banking, merger and acquisition advisory, institutional brokerage and research services through its subsidiaries. The company operates through two segments: Capital Markets and Principal Investing. The Capital Markets segment includes investment banking, institutional brokerage and research. It also provides investment banking services, including capital raising and financial advisory services for its corporate issuer clients, and institutional brokerage services including sales, trading, research, and securities lending services to its institutional investor clients. The Principal Investing segment activities consist primarily of investments in merchant banking and other equity investments, investment funds and corporate debt investments. The company was founded in June 2006 and is headquartered in Arlington, VA.                




Chief Financial Officer, Director & Executive Vice President

                                    2011 - 2013                


NGAS Resources, Inc.


                  NGAS Resources, Inc. explores and drills for natural gas properties. It specializes in generating its own geological prospects. The company was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Lexington, KY.                




